{"tid":577771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被揭買煙草股 美疾控中心主任辭職","createTime":"2018-03-02T04:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-03T10:28:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dbbd6e2e76bbd5873be1119dba05e8199e686ac5","tid":577771,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T04:55:55.000Z","msg":"美國疾病控制與預防中心（Centers for Disease Control and Prevention，CDC）主任菲茨杰拉德（Brenda Fitzgerald，圖右，法新社圖片）被揭發買入煙草股後，周三宣布辭職。<br />\n<br />\n菲茨杰拉德去年7月出掌CDC，政治網站Politico上日披露，她上任後一個月便買入日本煙草國際股票。據報道，她的煙草股組合還包括英美煙草、Imperial、Philip Morris及Altria 。煙草股只是投資組合一部分，她持股最多的是「股神」巴菲特旗下巴郡。<br />\n<br />\n買巴郡當然安全，但買煙草股卻危害飯碗，特別是對CDC的舵手而言。CDC的宣傳口號是「24/7：Saving Lives, Protecting People.」（救命護民，全年無休），預防吸煙引致的疾病是她的職責之一，買煙草股構成利益衝突。<br />\n<br />\n菲茨杰拉德是婦科醫生，曾擔任佐治亞州公共衞生部專員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://inews.hket.com/article/2003188/被揭買煙草股%20美疾控中心主任辭職\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2003188%2F%E8%A2%AB%E6%8F%AD%E8%B2%B7%E7%85%99%E8%8D%89%E8%82%A1%2520%E7%BE%8E%E7%96%BE%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%BB%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7&d=VsVLdbPc2yurNKMoUaw2rnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=47f883b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://inews.hket.com/article/2003188/被揭買煙草股%20美疾控中心主任辭職</a>"},{"pid":"dfc207d4c56832a1ddabc2f7beed7b8a3b37aade","tid":577771,"uid":63017,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T06:47:51.000Z","msg":"佢想逐步逐步收購之後私有化<br />\n之後唔再賣煙者"},{"pid":"39fc51a924bfec9816250e3d45189435fbff52af","tid":577771,"uid":22422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:13:56.000Z","msg":"對沖 識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f515f709de2dd3539432d0628355defaaf18712","tid":577771,"uid":6604,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"咁反支但買支資股 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr